<p>6:30 - 7:00&nbsp;pm British Columbia Sustainable Energy Association AGM</p>
<p>7:00 pm Screening of Watermark, a documentary from the filmmakers behind Manufactured Landscapes.&nbsp;The film shows water as a terraforming element and the scale of its reach, as well as the magnitude of our need and use. In <em>Watermark</em>, the viewer is immersed in a world defined by a magnificent force of nature that we all too often take for granted - until it's gone.</p>
